<section id="gtkscrolledwindow"><title>GTKScrolledWindow</title>
<para>The GTKScrolledWindow class is a subclass of the
GTKContainer class (<xref linkend="gtkcontainer" />).</para>

<para>This is a window widget with horizontal and vertical scroll bars.</para>

